(13, 'How should you explain a gap in your resume?', 'Make up a fake story', 'Be honest, explain the reason (e.g. health, skill-up period) and what you learned or achieved during that time', 'Refuse to answer the question', 'None of these', 'B'),
(13, 'What should you do if the interviewer corrects you during coding round?', 'Argue and try to prove them wrong', 'Listen to their feedback, evaluate the suggestion, thank them, and adjust your code accordingly', 'Panic and stop writing code', 'None of these', 'B'),
