(13, 'What should you do before starting to write code in a technical interview?', 'Start coding immediately to show speed', 'Ask clarifying questions to understand constraints, edge cases, and discuss the plan/approach', 'Write pseudocode in comments only', 'None of these', 'B'),
(13, 'What is the best way to handle technical stress during an interview?', 'Give up and say you cannot do it', 'Take a deep breath, break the problem into smaller parts, and speak your thought process out loud', 'Ask the interviewer to solve it', 'None of these', 'B'),
